sentence: Show me courses that involve parts of software engineering and artificial intelligence .
sentence-with-vars: Show me courses that involve parts of topic1 and topic0 .
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%artificial intelligence%" OR LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%software engineering%" ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%topic0%" OR LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%topic1%" ;
